                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"indent(2)\">I had hoped my good friend<lb/> to have seen you ere you left, but\n                as I presume<lb/> your engagements have prevented I beg you to<lb/> hand this letter\n                to <persName>Mrs. Hart</persName> with the deep assur-<lb/>ance of the friendship of\n                one long tried who will<lb/> ever be interested in your well being. May the<lb/> God\n                of <placeName>Israel</placeName> grant you success &amp; that you<lb/> may be able\n                to dispose your enemies like chaff<lb/> before the wind; leaving that marble\n                image<lb/> warms into life, not at the toil of the chisel but the<lb/> worship of\n                the sculptor &amp; I do trust that your toil<lb/> will be repaid by a full\n                appreciation of you by your<lb/> friends &amp; that your enemies even, will\n                admit<lb/> how much as followers of <placeName>Israel's</placeName> God they\n                are<lb/> indebted to you — If however disappointment &amp;<lb/> mortification shall\n                be the reward of your labor's<lb/> leave not I pray you the field of Literature\n                for<lb/> some less aspiring vocation — We cannot afford<lb/> to part with such a\n                champion; you have unf-<lb/>urled your banner to promote the Glory of<lb/> your\n                people, even when the even<add>?</add> hand of<lb/> persecution assails you still\n                let it flout trium<lb/>phantly to the glory of God! Remember my friend<lb/> we cease\n                to live when we no longer have some<lb/>-thing to do or to bear- unexpected\n                disappointm<lb/>ents crush the hopes &amp; <add>?</add> the plans of the most<lb/>\n                prosperous! Where is the individual upon whom</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p31z4290b/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
