                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>the cares of this world will not sometimes press<lb/> I hope that I shall soon hear\n                from you &amp;<lb/> of your triumph over your persecutions.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">May the God of <placeName>Israel</placeName> long preserve<lb/> you\n                to do his will is the sincere wish</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">of your friend. <persName role=\"author\">R. C. Moise</persName></p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
